productReviews.reviewText: This Avon, does exactly what it's suppose to do.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
My co-worker Bryton has one of these. He says it looks ragged.
My co-worker Atha has one of these. He says it looks narrow.
I tried to maul it but got onion all over it.
